USER-VISIBLE CHANGES (for detailed changes see ChangeLog in the source package)
--------------------

Version 1.0 (February 2009)
-------------

* The package now includes a vignette describing
  methodology and package. The package R source
  code is identical to versions 0.2-1 and 0.2-2.


Version 0.2 (December 2008)
-------------

* There will be an article in Journal of Statistical
  Software describing the package. This paper refers
  to version 0.2-1 of the package.


Version 0.1 (April 2008)
-------------

* First release.
